movie.title: BlacKkKlansman
movie.plot: Colorado Springs, late 1970s. Ron Stallworth, an African American police officer, and Flip Zimmerman, his Jewish colleague, run an undercover operation to infiltrate the Ku Klux Klan.

events.title: Amberley Snyder is paralysed in a car crash

movie.title: Walk. Ride. Rodeo.
movie.plot: Tells the incredible true story of Amberley Snyder, a nationally ranked rodeo barrel racer who defies the odds after barely surviving a car accident that leaves her paralyzed from the waist down.
